</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="510"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="510">The tax base and the units of measure for the tax base.</p>
