<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="512"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="512">The useful lifetime, in years, after the year of manufacture, and the
output year.</p>
