<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="515"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="515">The owned share as an indication that the vehicle is partially owned.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="517"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="517"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="517">Factor Kp</strong>  The increasing factor for expensive vehicles.</p>
