period. This factor is the ratio of the ownership period to the number
of calendar months in the period.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="523"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="523"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="523">Calculated advance payment / Tax</strong>  If the tax register is calculated
