<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="529"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="529"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="529">Exemption from tax</strong>  The code for the tax allowance as an exemption
