<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="532"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="532">The amount of the tax allowance as an exemption from tax.</p>
