</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="537"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="537"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="537">Allowance factor</strong>  The ratio of the grace period to the number of
