<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="540"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="540"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="540">Privilege</strong>  The code for the tax allowance as a reduction of the
