<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="548"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="548"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="548">Tax allowance amount</strong>  The amount of the tax deduction.</p>
