<h2 id="generate-a-transport-tax-declaration" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="640">Generate a transport tax declaration</h2>
<h3 id="set-up-the-system-to-generate-a-transport-tax-declaration" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-transport-tax-declaration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="642">Set up the system to generate a transport tax declaration</h3>
